This paper deals with neural network pruning, which is a topic that falls under the broad category of machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper specifically focuses on pruning techniques for computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) tasks. The paper also discusses the use of neural networks for optimization (cs.NE) and proposes a new technique for retraining (cs.AI). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.AI, and cs.CL.
